						p In the course of production activities at enterprises, in accordance with licenses for the right to handle waste, collection, transportation, processing, disposal, neutralization, placement of waste of hazard classes I – IV are implemented.
						p The amount of waste as of the beginning and end of each reporting year (waste remaining in accumulation) depends on the organization of the production process of processing the resulting waste. 
						p The presence of waste at the beginning of the year is 123,717,000 tonnes. During the reporting period, a partial liquidation of the sludge accumulator (Nizhnekamsk CHP LLC) was carried out. 
						p The total volume of processing (utilization) of the sludge accumulator amounted to 82,100 tonnes (LLC Nizhnekamsk CHP). Received waste from other economic entities-20,400 tonnes. Presence of waste at the end of the year is 43,300 tonnes.
