					.dmpage-text
						p JSC Taneco operates a specialized landfill for dumping waste products. The existing impervious screen made of a geosynthetic membrane (HDPE) excludes biological and chemical contamination of the adjacent territories, groundwater, and ensures the collection of leachate for its subsequent transportation to the treatment facilities. Waste placed in this way can be recovered for disposal when new recycling technologies become available.
						h2 DRILLING WASTE MANAGEMENT
						p Enterprises of the TATNEFT Group have formed and processed 94,997 tonnes of drilling waste. All waste generated during well drilling by contractors is the property of the Contractor according to the contractual terms and conditions. The Company has established a system for accounting and monitoring the movement of waste generated during drilling by contractors, as well as a system for compensating their costs for the disposal of drilling waste.
